# Secrets and local env files
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
!**/.env.example
!**/.env*.example

# Service accounts and credentials
**/serviceKey.json
**/serviceKey.local.json
**/service-account*.json
**/*credential*.json
**/*credentials*.json

# Common secret/cert formats
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/*.p12
**/*.pfx
**/*.crt
**/*.cer
**/*.jks
**/*.keystore
